                High Court shall determine which magistrate shall have jurisdiction under this
                section;

(g) in cases of total or partial intestacy, the names and
                addresses of all surviving spouses, children, parents, brothers and sisters of the
                deceased, and of the children of any child of his or hers then deceased;

